<div class="topic_details">
<h5><a href="?PHPSESSID=992e616df58c4135afa9fbba6c7c220a&amp;board=1963.0">Savage Pathfinder RPG</a> / <a href="?PHPSESSID=992e616df58c4135afa9fbba6c7c220a&amp;topic=127508.msg1130005#msg1130005" rel="nofollow">【扩展】【SWPF】【BestiaryⅠ】生物图鉴Ⅰ：天池蛇龙 TARN LINNORM</a></h5>
<span class="smalltext">&#171;&nbsp;最新帖子 由 <strong><a href="?PHPSESSID=992e616df58c4135afa9fbba6c7c220a&amp;action=profile;u=77809">白药君</a> </strong> 于<em> <strong>昨天</strong>19:56:27</em>&nbsp;&#187;</span>
</div>
<div class="list_posts"><sub><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/06/09/2ygV4f.png" alt="" width="16" height="20" class="bbc_img resized"/></sub> <span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong>天池蛇龙 TARN LINNORM【不羁角色】</strong></span></span><hr />这头噩梦般的巨型蛇龙具备一双同样恐怖的头颅，酸液和毒素在两张血盘大口内沸腾不已。尽管传说当中提及存在更为强大的蛇龙，然而在见证过生有双头的天池蛇龙能带来的浩劫后，鲜有人再能相信这点。天池蛇龙可以在山上黑暗深邃的湖泊当中沉睡数个世纪，即使是格拉里昂上最强大的英雄也会对这种真正的恐怖怪物心生畏惧。<hr /><strong>类别</strong>：邪恶龙类(天池蛇龙)<br><strong>属性</strong>：灵巧d12+1，聪慧d6，心魂d12，力量d12+10，活力d12+2<br><strong>技能</strong>：运动d12，格斗d12，察觉d12+2，潜行d10<br><strong>移速</strong>：7；<strong>格挡</strong>：8；<strong>坚韧</strong>：22(3)<br><strong>专长</strong>：奥法抗性，战斗反应，迅捷<br><strong>特殊能力</strong>：<br><ul class="bbc_list"><li><strong>全域视野</strong>：天池蛇龙能眼观六路，其忽略1点围攻加值。<li><strong>水栖</strong>：移速12<li><strong>护甲+3(重护甲)</strong>：复鳞外皮<li><strong>噬咬/爪抓</strong>：力量+d8，穿甲4。<li><strong>喷吐武器(酸)</strong>：锥形盖板，5d6伤害。对象下回合开始时会另外受到5d4的持续伤害。<li><strong>死亡诅咒(死亡)</strong>：任何杀死天池蛇龙的对象必须进行一次-4的心魂投骰来避免获得免疫(魔法<em>治疗</em>)。这个诅咒无法遭到<em>破法</em>。<li><strong>免疫</strong>：酸<li><strong>毒素(-4)</strong>：天池蛇龙的噬咬带有致命毒素。<li><strong>体型10(超大型)</strong>：这种蛇龙最长可达100英尺，重达24000磅，其能额外承受两个损伤。</ul><strong>语言</strong>：邪灵语，龙语，木族语<br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">TARN LINNORM<br>This nightmarishly gargantuan linnorm possesses two equally fearsome heads. Its twin jaws seethe with acid and poison. Although legends speak of even more powerful linnorms, it’s hard to believe after witnessing the devastation a two-headed tarn linnorm can wreak. Content to sleep away the centuries at the bottom of dark, deep mountain lakes, a tarn is a true horror feared by even the mightiest of heroes on Golarion.<br>Type: Evil Dragon (Tarn Linnorm)<br>Attributes: Agility d12+1, Smarts d6, Spirit d12, Strength d12+10, Vigor d12+2<br>Skills: Athletics d12, Fight- ing d12, Notice d12+2, Stealth d10<br>Pace: 7; Parry: 8; Tough- ness: 22 (3)<br>Edges: Arcane Resistance, Combat Reflexes, Quick<br>Special Abilities:<br>-All-Around Vision: Tarns can see in all directions. They ignore 1 point of Gang Up bonuses.<br>-Aquatic: Pace 12.<br>-Armor +3 (Heavy Armor): Scaly hide.<br>-Bite/Claws: Str+d8, AP 4.<br>-Breath Weapon (Acid): Cone Template, 5d6 damage. Lingering Damage inflicts another 5d4 at the start of the victim&#039;s next turn.<br>-Death Curse (Death): Anyone who slays a tarn linnorm must make a Spirit roll at –4 to resist acquiring an Immunity to magical healing. This curse can’t be dispelled.<br>-Immunity: Acid.<br>-Poison (–4): The tarn linnorm’s bite contains a Lethal poison.<br>-Size 10 (Huge): These linnorms are upwards of 100’ long and weigh 24,000 pounds. They can take two extra Wounds.<br>Languages: Aklo, Draconic, Sylvan.</div></div></div><br><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/08/17/f5r7pn.png" alt="" class="bbc_img"/><br><br><div class="quoteheader"><div class="topslice_quote">引用</div></div><blockquote class="bbc_standard_quote"><sub><img src="https://z3.ax1x.com/2021/06/09/2ygV4f.png" alt="" width="16" height="20" class="bbc_img resized"/></sub> <span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong>蛇龙绪论 LINNORM</strong></span></span><hr />蛇龙是出没于格拉里昂北部地区的原始龙类，它们的成长建立在对于自己眼中低等生物的憎恨之上，其总是想法设法尽可能地折磨那些不幸的受害者。通常栖息在偏僻地区的蛇龙能蛰伏上数个世纪，因此其破坏的欲望会随着世代交替而淡出视野——乃至于遭到遗忘。这些贪婪而饕餮的生物具备巨大的无翼蛇躯，喷吐武器，以及没有翅膀也能翱翔天际的内生魔法能力。最值得一提的是，所有蛇龙都具备同一种强大的防护能力，称之为&quot;死亡诅咒&quot;。<br><br><br><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong>通用能力 COMMON ABILITIES</strong></span></span><br><ul class="bbc_list"><li><strong>蛇龙</strong>：以18移速飞行；忽略所有照明减值；除非损伤是由寒铁制品造成，否则每轮都能尝试一次自然恢复投骰；源自寒铁武器的伤害+4；高级<em>侦测奥法</em>(所有调整)；免疫束缚与纠缠、寒冷，<em>诅咒</em>，<em>傀儡</em>，<em>幻象</em>，<em>隐形</em>，麻痹，毒素，<em>滞缓</em>，<em>沉眠</em>，震慑；以爪抓攻击时忽略4点尺寸减值。</ul><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">LINNORM<br>Linnorms are primeval dragons of the northern regions of Golarion. They thrive on their hatred for those they deem lesser creatures, and seek to inflict as much suffering as possible unto their unfortunate victims. Linnorms usually live in remote areas and hibernate for centuries, so their lust for devastation can go unnoticed—even forgotten—for generations. These greedy and gluttonous creatures have massive serpentine, wingless bodies. They all have breath weapons and an innate magical ability to fly, even without wings. Most notably, all linnorms share a potent defense, known as the Death Curse.<br><br>COMMON ABILITIES<br>-Linnorm: Fly at Pace 18; ignore all penalties for Illumination; may attempt a natural healing roll every round unless the Wounds were caused by cold iron objects; +4 damage from cold iron weapons; major detect arcana (all Modifiers); immune to Bound &amp;amp; Entangled, cold, curse, puppet, illusion, invisibility, paralysis, poison, sloth, slumber, Stun; ignore 4 points of Scale penalties when attacking with their claws.</div></div></div></blockquote><div class="quotefooter"><div class="botslice_quote"></div></div></div>
