%的概率使它们无效。这与其他类似的效果相叠加，例如护命甲fortification armor。<br><br><strong>火炬的报应（Nemesis of Torch）：</strong>尽管找到火炬大师是此次行动的目标，你也得到了助力来阻止这个神秘骗子。此boon对本模组的续集Society Scenario #10-23: Passing the Torch Part 2: Who Speaks for the Ten产生了影响。<br></div></div></div><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i>S10-23 传火Part2</i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;"><br></div></div></div></div>
